  "description": "Mod wheel sweeps feedback from clean space to the edge of self-oscillation. The figure-8 topology means feedback builds symmetrically — left and right loops reinforce each other at peak. A controlled swell that can be ridden expressively or pushed into glorious disarray. Aftertouch controls damping to prevent runaway.",
